(282, 'Site Update', 'No More Flash', '', 'Audifan is now 100% Flash free!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWe stopped using Flash for the Happy Box back in April.  Today, we''ve updated profile character icons and the garden timer sound system to use HTML5.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlease let us know if you find any issues.', 1480868305),
