(288, 'Site News', 'New Server!', '', 'Audifan will be moving to a shiny new server near the end of this month!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhat makes this server better than the current one?  A LOT of things, but here are the two biggest improvements:<br />\r\n<br />\r\n1. The new server will only host Audifan and its sister sites (other sites made by Mana Web Development).  Currently, Audifan is on a shared server, which is shared with about 20-30 other websites.  We''ve been very fortunate to have great server neighbors over the years and their sites haven''t caused any issues on Audifan.  However, this change ensures that the server will always prioritize Audifan.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2. HTTPS!  Our current hosting provider does not easily support HTTPS, but the new server provider does.  This means you will be able to use Audifan securely with an encrypted connection.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhen we officially move to the new server, the site will be taken down for a few hours as the new server address gets updated throughout the Internet.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAll of your account data will be moved over, so the switch should be relatively seamless.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe current plan is to make the switch on April 22, most likely in the evening.  We''ll announce a time once the date gets closer.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou can try the new server right now at <a href="https://staging.audifan.net">https://staging.audifan.net</a>!  Remember... everything you do on the test site will be deleted.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThank you for using Audifan.', 1491873312),
(289, 'Site Update', '4/22 Updates', '', '<ul>\r\n<li>Audifan has moved to a new server.  We''ll be closely monitoring the site for issues, but if you have any problems, please report them by sending us a message on Facebook or <a href="/tickets/">sending in a ticket</a>.</li>\r\n<li>HTTPS is now supported at <a href="https://audifan.net/">https://audifan.net</a>!</li>\r\n<li>The winner list on the VIP Drawing page will now update automatically after a drawing.</li>\r\n</ul>', 1492355571),
(290, 'Site Update', '4/23 Updates', '', '<ul>\r\n<li>Winning the Happy Box Jackpot will now give you a new Jackpot badge. It lasts until someone else wins!</li>\r\n<li>Fixed an issue where disconnecting your Facebook account and tying it to a new email address would make your account inaccessible.</li>\r\n</ul>', 1492960782),
(291, 'Site Update', '4/27 Updates', '', '<ul>\r\n<li>You can now change your IGN for quest submissions if you have not yet submitted any screenshots for the week.</li>\r\n<li>Fixed a display issue on the Battle Quest ranking if only one person participated the previous week.</li>\r\n</ul>', 1493344451),
