(298, 'Site Update', 'New No Ads Item Available', '', 'A new No Ads item can now be purchased at the <a href="/store/">Coin Store</a>!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThis item will remove advertisements from Audifan for one week. You must be logged in to disable ads.', 1509149989),
