(304, 'Site News', 'Thank You and Goodbye', '', 'Hello everyone,<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAs you''ve most likely noticed, the site has become extremely out of date and I''ve fallen behind with the most recent updates.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI started Audifan back in 2007 when I was in high school, and I played Audition almost every second of my spare time.  I decided to combine my love for Audition and coding to create Audifan, and it eventually grew into what it is today.  My goal from the start was never to make a profit off the site.  I just wanted to make a site that I thought was cool and useful for myself and other players.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHowever, fast forward eleven years to today, and I haven''t played the game in almost two years.  And, honestly, I can''t really be invested in maintaining a site for a game that I don''t play anymore.  Therefore, unfortunately, I feel it''s time for me to start winding-down the site.  As of today, I will be "freezing" Audifan.  Any existing content will remain as-is, but features that require an administrator (Quests and the VIP Drawing) have been discontinued.  Also, I will work on sending out the remaining VIP Drawing prizes that haven''t been sent out yet.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAudifan will be taken offline this summer.  I''ll announce a specific date when the time gets nearer.  The code used on the site will be added to GitHub, if anyone would like to use any of it.  No account information will be included.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nI want to thank every person who helped me along the way.  Everyone who gave suggestions.  Everyone who helped test new features.  Everyone who helped grade quest submissions.  Everyone who sent corrections.  Everyone who recorded song times.  Everyone who simply logged in and gave the site their attention for a few minutes each day.  I''ve had so much fun along the way, and you guys are awesome!  I may have built the site, but just as a house becomes a home, so does a website become a community.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGoodbye and good luck!', 1520054491),
(305, 'Site News', 'Audifan Will Be Taken Down on June 18', 'https://audifan.net/news/view/304/', '', 1527125433);
